<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %> - Sistema de Produtos</title>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Font Awesome -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <!-- Google Fonts -->
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Baskerville:wght@400;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navegação -->
    <%- include('partials/navbar') %>
    
    <!-- Mensagens Flash -->
    <%- include('partials/flash-messages') %>
    
    <!-- Conteúdo Principal -->
    <main class="container-fluid px-4 py-4">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-lg-8">
                <div class="card border-0 shadow-sm">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white py-3">
                        <h2 class="card-title mb-0 fw-bold">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle me-2"></i>
                            Sobre o Sistema
                        </h2>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body p-4">
                        <p class="lead text-muted mb-4">
                            Sistema de Gerenciamento de Produtos desenvolvido com as mais modernas tecnologias web.
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="row mb-4">
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-cogs me-2"></i>
                                    Tecnologias Utilizadas
                                </h5>
                                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fab fa-node-js text-success me-3 fa-lg"></i>
                                        <div>
                                            <strong>Node.js</strong>
                                            <small class="d-block text-muted">Runtime JavaScript</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-server text-primary me-3 fa-lg"></i>
                                        <div>
                                            <strong>Express.js</strong>
                                            <small class="d-block text-muted">Framework web</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-code text-info me-3 fa-lg"></i>
                                        <div>
                                            <strong>EJS</strong>
                                            <small class="d-block text-muted">Template engine</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-database text-warning me-3 fa-lg"></i>
                                        <div>
                                            <strong>Sequelize</strong>
                                            <small class="d-block text-muted">ORM para banco de dados</small>
                                        </div>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            
                            <div class="col-md-6">
                                <h5 class="fw-bold text-primary mb-3">
                                    <i class="fas fa-list-check me-2"></i>
                                    Funcionalidades
                                </h5>
                                <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-plus-circle text-success me-3"></i>
                                        Cadastro de produtos
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-edit text-primary me-3"></i>
                                        Edição de dados
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-eye text-info me-3"></i>
                                        Visualização detalhada
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-trash text-danger me-3"></i>
                                        Exclusão de registros
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="list-group-item d-flex align-items-center">
                                        <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-secondary me-3"></i>
                                        Interface responsiva
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="alert alert-info border-0" role="alert">
                            <h6 class="alert-heading fw-bold">
                                <i class="fas fa-lightbulb me-2"></i>
                                Características do Sistema
                            </h6>
                            <p class="mb-0">
                                Este sistema demonstra a implementação completa de operações CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) 
                                utilizando as melhores práticas de desenvolvimento web com Node.js, incluindo validação de dados, 
                                tratamento de erros, interface responsiva e arquitetura MVC.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                            <a href="/produtos" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg me-3">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right me-2"></i>
                                Acessar Sistema
                            </a>
                            <a href="/" class="btn btn-outline-secondary btn-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i>
                                Voltar ao Início
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
    
    <!-- Rodapé -->
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    
    <!-- Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>

